data.description: Put this home on your MUST SEE LIST!  Assumable VA LOAN at 2.78%! Recent upgrades include: RV Pad w/ 30 amp outlet; vinyl replcmnt windows in 2022, xeriscaped yard, 2 yr old washer/dryer/SS dishwasher. Add'l updating: Roof  replaced in 2015, stucco redone in 2016, AC unit replaced in 2021, kitchn & baths are remodeled too. * NO POLY PIPE*NO HOA*NO PID* .Extensive work completed in front & backyards; xeriscaping, install of pet turf,  bee/butterfly garden, wall height increased, side yard wall+ gate installation & more.  Storage shed discreetly placed in back yard.  Large patio area with hot tub & retractable awning. Energy savings due to solar panels. Ave. monthly payment to SunRUn is $95+$8 for PNM.  Can't beat those energy costs! Home is clean and ready to go!  Just unpack and ENJOY!
